---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Policy & Frameworks" description="Analysis of AI governance frameworks, regulatory policy, and integration considerations for practitioners.">
  <style>
    .page-header { padding: clamp(4rem,8vw,6rem) clamp(1.5rem,5vw,5rem) 3rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
    .page-kicker { font-size: 0.62rem; letter-spacing: 0.22em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--gold); margin-bottom: 1.25rem; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; }
    .page-kicker::before { content: ''; width: 24px; height: 1px; background: var(--gold-dim); display: block; }
    .page-title { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: clamp(3rem,6vw,5rem); font-weight: 300; line-height: 1; color: var(--text-primary); letter-spacing: -0.02em; margin-bottom: 1.25rem; }
    .page-desc { font-size: 1rem; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.8; max-width: 600px; }
    .policy-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0; border: 1px solid var(--border); margin: 4rem 0; }
    .policy-item { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 80px 1fr auto; align-items: start; gap: 2rem; padding: 1.75rem 2rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); cursor: pointer; transition: background 0.2s; text-decoration: none; color: inherit; }
    .policy-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
    .policy-item:hover { background: var(--bg-card); }
    .policy-num { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 2.5rem; font-weight: 300; color: var(--text-muted); opacity: 0.35; line-height: 1; padding-top: 3px; }
    .policy-content h3 { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 1.3rem; font-weight: 400; color: var(--text-primary); margin-bottom: 0.4rem; line-height: 1.25; }
    .policy-content p { font-size: 0.83rem; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.7; max-width: 560px; }
    .policy-meta { display: flex; gap: 1rem; margin-top: 0.75rem; font-size: 0.62rem; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--text-muted); }
    .policy-tags { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.4rem; align-items: flex-end; }
    .coming-soon { padding: 4rem; text-align: center; background: var(--bg-card); border: 1px solid var(--border); margin: 4rem 0; }
    .coming-soon h3 { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 400; color: var(--text-primary); margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
    .coming-soon p { font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.75; }
    @media(max-width:600px){.policy-item{grid-template-columns:40px 1fr;}.policy-tags{display:none;}}
  </style>

  <div class="page-header">
    <div class="page-kicker">Analysis & Research</div>
    <h1 class="page-title">Policy & Frameworks</h1>
    <p class="page-desc">Careful reading of emerging AI policy — from the EU to India to the UN — with practical implications for practitioners and organizational leaders.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="container">
    <div class="coming-soon">
      <h3>Policy posts coming soon</h3>
      <p>Axiom Review is preparing its first series of policy analysis pieces on AI governance frameworks including the EU AI Act, NIST RMF, and India's DPDP Act. Drop your email below to be notified when the first piece publishes.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Placeholder policy items to show the structure -->
    <div class="policy-list">
      <div class="policy-item" style="opacity:0.4;cursor:default;">
        <div class="policy-num">01</div>
        <div class="policy-content">
          <span class="card-tag policy">Comparative Analysis</span>
          <h3>EU AI Act vs. NIST RMF: A Practitioner's Comparison</h3>
          <p>A structured side-by-side analysis of the two dominant frameworks shaping enterprise AI governance, with practical recommendations for multi-jurisdictional organizations.</p>
          <div class="policy-meta"><span>Coming soon</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="policy-tags"><span class="card-tag policy">EU AI Act</span><span class="card-tag">NIST</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="policy-item" style="opacity:0.4;cursor:default;">
        <div class="policy-num">02</div>
        <div class="policy-content">
          <span class="card-tag">Framework Deep-Dive</span>
          <h3>The OECD AI Principles at Five Years: Impact and Gaps</h3>
          <p>Reviewing the adoption and practical influence of the OECD's foundational principles across G20 economies, and identifying the gaps that more binding legislation must fill.</p>
          <div class="policy-meta"><span>Coming soon</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="policy-tags"><span class="card-tag">OECD</span><span class="card-tag policy">G20</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="policy-item" style="opacity:0.4;cursor:default;">
        <div class="policy-num">03</div>
        <div class="policy-content">
          <span class="card-tag policy">Emerging Regulation</span>
          <h3>India's DPDP Act and Its Implications for AI Systems</h3>
          <p>India's Digital Personal Data Protection Act introduces compliance obligations that directly shape how AI systems can collect, process, and retain personal data.</p>
          <div class="policy-meta"><span>Coming soon</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="policy-tags"><span class="card-tag">DPDP</span><span class="card-tag policy">India</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
